holidays, work, love,

327
00:22:13.760 --> 00:22:21.050
time, household items, weather, music,
politics, feelings, goals, etc.

328
00:22:21.120 --> 00:22:26.040
And so this is going to give you
a very wide range of vocabulary.

329
00:22:26.040 --> 00:22:27.930
You're going to listen
to a lot of different words.

330
00:22:28.000 --> 00:22:32.530
And for each story, you're going to notice
