if you take classes at the university,

711
00:43:04.880 --> 00:43:08.050
if you're doing a bunch
of different things, stop doing that.

712
00:43:08.120 --> 00:43:11.600
Only focus on RAIO, laser focus.

713
00:43:11.840 --> 00:43:14.410
That's going to help you
learn faster as well.

714
00:43:14.480 --> 00:43:20.320
I get this question a lot,
"Kale, should I listen to music

715
00:43:20.320 --> 00:43:23.240
and should I watch movies
