717
00:43:24.840 --> 00:43:26.810
No, you should not.

718
00:43:26.880 --> 00:43:28.650
Focus only on RAIO.

719
00:43:28.720 --> 00:43:31.330
If you want to watch
movies in English, do that.

720
00:43:31.400 --> 00:43:34.450
But it's not going to be
part of your learning, yet.

721
00:43:34.520 --> 00:43:35.570
Further on.

722
00:43:35.640 --> 00:43:37.970
Focus 100% on RAIO.

723
00:43:38.040 --> 00:43:39.280
One section a day.

724
00:43:39.310 --> 00:43:42.210
Try to finish a section a day,
