854
00:50:41.600 --> 00:50:46.160
So you need to be able to speak
and interact in English without the fear

855
00:50:46.230 --> 00:50:50.210
of anyone judging you or correcting you.

856
00:50:50.280 --> 00:50:55.130
Error correction is actually done
automatically through input.

857
00:50:55.200 --> 00:50:59.290
So if you want to have better grammar,
you need to consume more good grammar.

858
00:50:59.360 --> 00:51:01.530
And you're going to automatically
correct yourself.

859
00:51:01.600 --> 00:51:04.610
If you have children, this
is exactly how it works with them

860
00:51:04.680 --> 00:51:07.570
and how it worked for you as well
when you learned Spanish as a child.

861
00:51:07.640 --> 00:51:12.560
You didn't correct your own mistakes
as a child by listening to

862
00:51:12.560 --> 00:51:13.770
