The only apology that I accept is, "I'm
sorry, Kale, I haven't studied enough."

888
00:52:22.160 --> 00:52:23.610
That's a good apology.

889
00:52:23.680 --> 00:52:26.080
But if you say, "I'm sorry,
I'm bad at English" or "I'm bad

890
00:52:26.150 --> 00:52:27.730
