892
00:52:29.160 --> 00:52:30.850
You just haven't consumed enough.

893
00:52:30.920 --> 00:52:32.090
That's what you're going to do here.

894
00:52:32.160 --> 00:52:34.730
Rule number 15,
the only failure is stopping.

895
00:52:34.800 --> 00:52:37.610
So don't stop.
Continue over and over again.

896
00:52:37.680 --> 00:52:44.810
If you have a week where you stop
